                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290409-315-off1776 t18290409-315-cd1777"></join>, 1 cloak, value 7s.; 1 gown, value 1s, 6d., and 1 pair of shoes, value 1s. 6d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18290409-315-victim2873" type="victimName">
                           William 
